{
  "texts": [
    "H and O denote the number of attention heads and sampling points, respectively.",
    "Each head refines sampling positions using offsets (∆x iho, ∆y iho, ∆z iho), weighted by attention scores α iho.",
    "Learnable matrices W h and W ′ h transform query and voxel features.",
    "This process guides queries to informative 3D regions, enhancing spatial and depth representations.",
    "Dynamic Query Aggregation (DQA)."
  ]
}